A [[en/Community/Patches/Patches]] that helps you managing trains by reporting vehicle as '''lost''' if the station it is currently heading to has not been reached in this amount of time.

== Use ==
You can set peroid of time needed for warning message to pop up via [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Vehicles|configure patches window]] or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:

<pre>
[patches]
lost_train_days = 180
</pre>



